OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy day with
OL,6,Foccasional rain, heavy and thundery at
OL,7,Ftimes. There will be some drier spells
OL,8,Fof weather too. Warm and humid with
OL,9,Flight winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FShowers slowly dying out but
OL,12,Fquite a cloudy evening in places with
OL,13,Fsome mist and fog possible. Winds
OL,14,Fstrengthening overnight and feeling
OL,15,Fquite muggy and warm.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FA cloudy start to the
OL,18,Fweekend, windy and feeling warm, some
OL,19,Fshowers developing for Argyll in the
OL,20,Fafternoon and perhaps all areas in the
OL,21,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
